msgstr "通过节点层次结构，管理游戏循环。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:19
msgid ""
"As one of the most important classes, the ``SceneTree`` manages the "
"hierarchy of nodes in a scene as well as scenes themselves. Nodes can be "
"added, retrieved and removed. The whole scene tree (and thus the current "
"scene) can be paused. Scenes can be loaded, switched and reloaded."
msgstr ""
"作为最重要的类之一，``SceneTree`` "
"管理场景中节点的层次以及场景本身。可以添加、检索和删除节点。整个场景树（以及当前场景）都可以暂停。可以加载、切换和重新加载场景。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:21
msgid ""
"You can also use the ``SceneTree`` to organize your nodes into groups: "
"every node can be assigned as many groups as you want to create, e.g. a "
"\"enemy\" group. You can then iterate these groups or even call methods "
"and set properties on all the group's members at once."
msgstr ""
"您还可以使用 ``SceneTree`` 将节点组织到编组：您可以为每个节点分配任意数量的编组，例如 一个 ``敌人`` "
"编组。然后，您可以迭代这些编组，甚至调用方法，并一次在编组的所有成员上设置属性。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:23
msgid ""
"``SceneTree`` is the default :ref:`MainLoop <class_MainLoop>` "
"implementation used by scenes, and is thus in charge of the game loop."
msgstr "``SceneTree`` 是场景使用的默认 :ref:`MainLoop <class_MainLoop>` 实现，因此负责游戏循环。"

