#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:250
msgid "enum **GroupCallFlags**:"
msgstr "枚举 **GroupCallFlags**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:252
msgid "**GROUP_CALL_DEFAULT** = **0** --- Call a group with no flags (default)."
msgstr "**GROUP_CALL_DEFAULT** = **0** —— 无标志调用一个编组组（默认）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:254
msgid "**GROUP_CALL_REVERSE** = **1** --- Call a group in reverse scene order."
msgstr "**GROUP_CALL_REVERSE** = **1** —— 以相反的场景顺序调用一个编组。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:256
msgid ""
"**GROUP_CALL_REALTIME** = **2** --- Call a group immediately (calls are "
"normally made on idle)."
msgstr "**GROUP_CALL_REALTIME** = **2** —— 立即调用一个编组（调用通常在空闲状态下进行）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:258
msgid ""
"**GROUP_CALL_UNIQUE** = **4** --- Call a group only once even if the call"
" is executed many times."
msgstr "**GROUP_CALL_UNIQUE** = **4** —— 即使调用已执行多次，也只能调用一个编组一次。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:270
msgid "enum **StretchMode**:"
msgstr "枚举 **StretchMode**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:272
msgid "**STRETCH_MODE_DISABLED** = **0** --- No stretching."
msgstr "**STRETCH_MODE_DISABLED** = **0** —— 不能伸展。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:274
msgid ""
"**STRETCH_MODE_2D** = **1** --- Render stretching in higher resolution "
"(interpolated)."
msgstr "**STRETCH_MODE_2D** = **1** —— 以更高的分辨率渲染拉伸（插值）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:276
msgid ""
"**STRETCH_MODE_VIEWPORT** = **2** --- Keep the specified display "
"resolution. No interpolation. Content may appear pixelated."
msgstr "**STRETCH_MODE_VIEWPORT** = **2** —— 保持指定的显示分辨率。无插值。内容可能显示为像素化。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:292
msgid "enum **StretchAspect**:"
msgstr "枚举 **StretchAspect**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:294
msgid ""
"**STRETCH_ASPECT_IGNORE** = **0** --- Fill the window with the content "
"stretched to cover excessive space. Content may appear stretched."
msgstr "**STRETCH_ASPECT_IGNORE** = **0** —— 填充窗口使用拉伸内容以覆盖过多的空间。内容可能看起来被拉伸。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:296
msgid ""
"**STRETCH_ASPECT_KEEP** = **1** --- Retain the same aspect ratio by "
"padding with black bars on either axis. This prevents distortion."
msgstr "**STRETCH_ASPECT_KEEP** = **1** —— 通过在任一轴上填充黑条来保持相同的宽高比。这样可以防止失真。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:298
msgid ""
"**STRETCH_ASPECT_KEEP_WIDTH** = **2** --- Expand vertically. Left/right "
"black bars may appear if the window is too wide."
msgstr "**STRETCH_ASPECT_KEEP_WIDTH** = **2** —— 垂直展开。如果窗口太宽，则可能会出现左/右黑条。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:300
msgid ""
"**STRETCH_ASPECT_KEEP_HEIGHT** = **3** --- Expand horizontally. "
"Top/bottom black bars may appear if the window is too tall."
msgstr "**STRETCH_ASPECT_KEEP_HEIGHT** = **3** —— 水平展开。如果窗口太高，则可能会出现顶部/底部的黑条。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_scenetree.rst:302
msgid ""
"**STRETCH_ASPECT_EXPAND** = **4** --- Expand in both directions, "
"retaining the same aspect ratio. This prevents distortion while avoiding "
"black bars."
msgstr "**STRETCH_ASPECT_EXPAND** = **4** —— 沿两个方向扩展，保持相同的纵横比。这样可以防止变形，同时避免黑条。"

